==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wakeful
<hw>Wake"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not sleeping;
indisposed to sleep; watchful; vigilant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Dissembling sleep, but <qex>wakeful</qex> with the fright.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Wake"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Wake"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waken</ent>⟦br⟧
